     -------------------------------------------------------------------------
     SKU PATTERN (per Active_SKUs sheet + datasheet page 3 + James 2026-05-02 PM):
       LSBX3W&#123;150|300&#125;-3H1-&#123;U|H&#125;&#123;D|B|S|W|RAL####&#125;&#123;3|4|5&#125;/RB3&#123;/RS|/TN|/UA|/SP?&#125;{/PS?}{/MSP-XXX?}
